OL,3,CAndy Burnham becomes UK's 7th prime
OL,4,Cminister in a decade - how did we get
OL,5,Chere?
OL,7,FBy ITV News Producer Hannah Ward-
OL,8,FGlenton
OL,10,FAndy Burnham has become the seventh
OL,11,FBritish prime minister in just over a
OL,12,Fdecade.
OL,14,FIf it feels as though tenures in No 10
OL,15,Fhave got shorter, it's because they
OL,16,Fhave - between 1966 and 2016, leaders
OL,17,Fheld the top job for an average of six
OL,18,For seven years, with Margaret Thatcher
OL,19,Fleading the country for almost 12.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784569706
OL,3,CAndy Burnham becomes UK's 7th prime
OL,4,Cminister in a decade - how did we get
OL,5,Chere?
OL,7,FBut it has been a different story in
OL,8,Fthe last 10 years: from 2016 to 2026,
OL,9,Fleadership cycles have averaged around
OL,10,Ftwo years, a period that includes the
OL,11,FUK's shortest-serving PM at just 49
OL,12,Fdays - Liz Truss.
OL,14,FWith the former Mayor of Greater
OL,15,FManchester now handed the well-worn
OL,16,Fkeys to No 10, ITV News looks back at
OL,17,Fthe previous PMs and their downfall.
OL,19,FDavid Cameron (May 2010 - July 2016)
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784569706
OL,3,CAndy Burnham becomes UK's 7th prime
OL,4,Cminister in a decade - how did we get
OL,5,Chere?
OL,7,FWhile David Cameron had a lengthy
OL,8,Fstint as PM compared to his
OL,9,Fsuccessors, his decision to resign in
OL,10,Fthe wake of the Brexit vote is widely
OL,11,Fseen as the start of the "revolving
OL,12,Fdoor" at No 10.
OL,14,FUnder his leadership, the
OL,15,FConservatives ended a 13-year run of
OL,16,FLabour government in the 2010 election
OL,17,F` though they failed to win a majority
OL,18,Fand were forced to enter a coalition
OL,19,Fwith the Liberal Democrats.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784569706
OL,3,CAndy Burnham becomes UK's 7th prime
OL,4,Cminister in a decade - how did we get
OL,5,Chere?
OL,7,FWhile the coalition struggled with
OL,8,Finfighting between the two parties,
OL,9,Fthe Conservatives also faced growing
OL,10,Fpressure from Nigel Farage's
OL,11,FEurosceptic Ukip, which pledged to
OL,12,Ftake the UK out of the EU.
OL,14,FCameron had agreed to a referendum on
OL,15,Fthe UK's membership of the European
OL,16,FUnion, but when the nation narrowly
OL,17,Fvoted to leave, the pro-remain prime
OL,18,Fminister decided it was time to end
OL,19,Fhis tenure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784569706
OL,3,CAndy Burnham becomes UK's 7th prime
OL,4,Cminister in a decade - how did we get
OL,5,Chere?
OL,7,F"I do not think it would be right for
OL,8,Fme to be the captain that steers our
OL,9,Fcountry to its next destination," he
OL,10,Fsaid in a statement outside Downing
OL,11,FStreet.
OL,13,FInitiating the Brexit referendum
OL,14,Fbecame one of the defining moments of
OL,15,FCameron's career, but he is also
OL,16,Fcredited with having formed and led
OL,17,Fthe first UK coalition government
OL,18,Fsince the Second World War and
OL,19,Foverseeing the legalisation of same-
OL,20,Fsex marriage in England and Wales.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31606
