CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784569706
OL,3,CAndy Burnham becomes UK's 7th prime
OL,4,Cminister in a decade - how did we get
OL,5,Chere?
OL,7,FCameron also signed off on deep public
OL,8,Fspending cuts following the 2008
OL,9,Ffinancial crisis.
OL,11,FTheresa May (July 2016 - July 2019)
OL,13,FTheresa May picked up the Brexit
OL,14,Fmantle and it dominated her time as
OL,15,Fprime minister as she tried to deliver
OL,16,Fa deal that would satisfy both sides
OL,17,Fof the divided Conservative Party and
OL,18,Fthe country more widely.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
