OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784569706
OL,3,CAndy Burnham becomes UK's 7th prime
OL,4,Cminister in a decade - how did we get
OL,5,Chere?
OL,7,FAfter a lot of back and forth,
OL,8,FBritain's second female PM almost
OL,9,Fsucceeded in securing a deal in 2018,
OL,10,Fbut lost the support of key members of
OL,11,Fher cabinet and later that year faced
OL,12,Fa no-confidence vote, which she won.
OL,14,FBut opposition to her leadership
OL,15,Fremained strong and variations of her
OL,16,Fdeal were shot down by MPs, prompting
OL,17,Fher to resign in March 2024.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
