PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784569706
OL,3,CAndy Burnham becomes UK's 7th prime
OL,4,Cminister in a decade - how did we get
OL,5,Chere?
OL,7,FJust months after coming to power with
OL,8,Fa huge majority, Johnson made a
OL,9,Ftelevised address announcing a
OL,10,Fnationwide lockdown as Covid-19
OL,11,Freached UK shores. A month later,
OL,12,FJohnson himself tested positive for
OL,13,Fcoronavirus and became so ill that he
OL,14,Fspent several days in intensive care.
OL,16,FAs the UK emerged from lockdown,
OL,17,FJohnson's government was hit by a
OL,18,Fseries of scandals and revelations
OL,19,Fduring the pandemic that became known
OL,20,Fas Partygate, which ultimately led to
OL,21,Fhis downfall.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784569706
OL,3,CAndy Burnham becomes UK's 7th prime
OL,4,Cminister in a decade - how did we get
OL,5,Chere?
OL,7,FHis chief advisor Dominic Cummings was
OL,8,Faccused of breaking lockdown rules by
OL,9,Fdriving to Barnard Castle, ITV News
OL,10,Frevealed evidence of illicit meet-ups
OL,11,Fduring the height of lockdown, Johnson
OL,12,Fbecame the first sitting prime
OL,13,Fminister fined by the police for
OL,14,Fbreaking the law, and he denied
OL,15,Fknowledge of sexual assault
OL,16,Fallegations against MP Chris Pincher,
OL,17,Fdespite having been aware of what was
OL,18,Fhappening, to list some of the
OL,19,Fscandals that unfurled during
OL,20,FJohnson's stint in office.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
