PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784569706
OL,3,CAndy Burnham becomes UK's 7th prime
OL,4,Cminister in a decade - how did we get
OL,5,Chere?
OL,7,FAfter three years and 43 days in
OL,8,Fpower, Johnson announced his
OL,9,Fresignation outside Downing Street,
OL,10,Fsaying he wanted Britons to "know how
OL,11,Fsad (he is) to be giving up the best
OL,12,Fjob in the world - but them's the
OL,13,Fbreaks".
OL,15,FHe didn't show much remorse over the
OL,16,Fcircumstances that led to his
OL,17,Fresignation, suggesting he'd been
OL,18,Fforced out by a "herd instinct" in
OL,19,FWestminster which was too "powerful"
OL,20,Fto resist.
OL,26,@sD@EpmsD@Kpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/21
