OL,3,CAndy Burnham becomes UK's 7th prime
OL,4,Cminister in a decade - how did we get
OL,5,Chere?
OL,7,FHe did deliver on some of his goals,
OL,8,Fincluding bringing NHS England waiting
OL,9,Flists down to their lowest levels in
OL,10,Fnearly four years and reducing net
OL,11,Fmigration.
OL,13,FAndy Burnham (July 2026 - ?)
OL,15,FAndy Burnham takes over as prime
OL,16,Fminister on Monday. So far he has
OL,17,Fpromised to be "unashamedly Labour" as
OL,18,Fa leader and to have the "courage to
OL,19,Ffix the big things that politics has
OL,20,Fneglected".
